Digital Portfolio

Platforms Set Up: For my digital portfolio, I set up GitHub, LinkedIn, and Stack Overflow. GitHub hosts my projects, code, and case studies in an organized way. LinkedIn helps me build a professional network and showcase my skills. Stack Overflow allows me to practice problem-solving, ask questions, and learn from a global developer community.

Reflection: Setting up these platforms taught me how to present my work professionally, improve digital organization, and engage with online communities. It boosted my confidence in sharing my projects, strengthened my coding and networking skills, and prepared me for future academic and career opportunities.
